{"tid":755084,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣吸收足夠既蛋白質？","createTime":"2018-07-25T02:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T19:19:53.000Z","uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"51ebd8c0c7c41873d04bd7f750bd54d1beb31d62","tid":755084,"uid":170062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"請問各位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小妹近排想瘦身，check咗身體機能<br />\n肌肉量過少脂肪過多，<br />\n近排加操核心訓練（Hiit, 7分鐘運動之類）<br />\n但覺得成效唔係好大<br />\n諗諗下 可能係蛋白質吸收唔夠多<br />\n上網睇過我大慨需要吸收75-100克蛋白質<br />\n（我重50公斤）<br />\n<br />\n請問各位大佬，只靠天然食物 <br />\n點樣可以吸收足100克呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無咩配搭可以俾小妹參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f28ba5a031aaf0bfd9903dfc80132f9417ca41","tid":755084,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51ebd8c0c7c41873d04bd7f750bd54d1beb31d62","tid":755084,"uid":170062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"請問各位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小妹近排想瘦身，check咗身體機能<br />\n肌肉量過少脂肪過多，<br />\n近排加操核心訓練（Hiit, 7分鐘運動之類）<br />\n但覺得成效唔係好大<br />\n諗諗下 可能係蛋白質吸收唔夠多<br />\n上網睇過我大慨需要吸收75-100克蛋白質<br />\n（我重50公斤）<br />\n<br />\n請問各位大佬，只靠天然食物 <br />\n點樣可以吸收足100克呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無咩配搭可以俾小妹參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"食蛋<img src=\"/assets/fa